reviewText: Equal to the Jock Cousteau Series

If you want the slickest photography, look elsewhere. If you want Real, hardcore ocean exploration with grit, heart and a Zissou-esque soundtrack, you need this set.
It appears to have been made in the 80s, as the mustaches and back hair on most of the divers will attest. But it's fun, exciting and educational, that is, better than 99% if the DVDs you could buy
